{"title":"张庄村的和平签名","authors":["毕耀彩"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"张庄村的和平签名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕耀彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人嘶喊，锣鼓敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张庄签名开始了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村主席大声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“反对新战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要和平！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁赞成快来签名。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张老汉急的通身汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起锄头转回庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过大街走小巷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上走到会场上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众围的严又严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人民齐声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要签名！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会写的用笔写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会写的用嘴来报名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍白胡子张老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进会场喊一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“乡亲们，闪一闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我签上名！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姓张，叫玉山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛过长活，要过饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土改以后把身翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心一意搞生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义要想挑动战争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那可不沾！（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不怕原子弹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起锄头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打退美国侵略者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的大儿是个买卖人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国飞机扔炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大儿在石家庄遭了难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死了尸骨都没见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二儿生气上前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替兄报仇到江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒日本鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋贼也完蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要和平过日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要发家搞生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾的人民也要得解放！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张老汉把笔放下话说完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿媳妇抱着孙子在后边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿媳妇叫一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爹！写上我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我男人报仇恨！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话声音变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪雨一般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爹！记着写上你孙子的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的名字叫胜利。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对！全家七口都写上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多力量大如山！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千人写，万人说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"签名簿上都写满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身农民觉悟高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界大事都要管！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“反对新战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决保卫世界和平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：“那可不成”的意思。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}